<p>The salient features of Simple Banners are:</p>
<ol>
<li>Easy to Manage with Magento Backend Admin management </li>
<li>Front end is Flash Flash Enabled for Sliding and blur effect.</li>
<li>Easy to Customize</li>
<li>Easy to Install; Easy to upgrade; Just copy to use </li>
<li>Banner Block (A banner can be displayed anywhere within a CMS page by putting a block in it.)</li>
<li>When Adding or Editing a banner you have the following Options: Banner Title</li>
<li>Banner Configuration including General Setting, Text Setting, Transition Setting, Show Hide Setting</li>
</ol>
<p>Simple Banners will help you:</p>
<ol>
<li>Manage your banners campaigns</li>
<li>Target specific customers groups</li>
<li>Display your payments and security icons</li>
<li>Display scheduled events information and holidays related content</li>
<li>Display special hours content info</li>
</ol>
